The goal of this study is to compare the efficacy of PVI irrigation to no irrigation for decreasing postoperative intra-abdominal abscesses in children with perforated appendicitis.

 Additionally, this study aims to verify the safety profile of dilute PVI for intra-abdominal irrigation.

